{"tid":400693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真-無事，or，真-帽事？","createTime":"2017-09-15T04:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T06:48:42.000Z","uid":147106,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c15774040dbdf90b8dd1e85c35f97ec24ebedf0b","tid":400693,"uid":147106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:25:52.000Z","msg":"琴日睇另一個po 有人話&quot;<span style=\"color: gold;\">未分手同其他人曖昧/wts，分左即刻同第個一齊，都係帽</span>&quot; 我即刻諗 我係米<ins>被帽而不自知</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢(Ex)一齊10個月<br />\n佢無公開過我 手機永遠有幾個聲稱&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">識左好耐好好感情</span>&quot; &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">一定唔會有野</span>&quot;既紅顏知己<br />\n好多時候做乜都同佢地分享 我身邊D fd經常性同我講&quot;<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>事既&quot;<br />\n我愛佢所以選擇百分百信佢 佢話無野 米無野<br />\n直到分左手 佢老尾 又開po又呢樣又個樣 佢個d所謂既紅顏知己先知佢拍過拖<br />\n講到自己好專一又好深情 <br />\n<br />\n分左手都5知有無一個月 同左個青梅竹馬(我完全5知有呢個人存在)一齊 仲要轉合照又乜又乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌 最可笑既係 到呢個moment 我都未放得低佢 仲等緊佢番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打們 我係米真係被<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80227b834008fb9a4ab9306363377f3b76ba893","tid":400693,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"米你老母"},{"pid":"3a00117e9d60a412e9305e549a3c1c55be282cbf","tid":400693,"uid":2833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8f65b61470c6ef1503e66dba1faf19d3fb97bc","tid":400693,"uid":24319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b2ee91bd739318dfb28e97db306cff3c34247c","tid":400693,"uid":122596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,